title: X-Men - Age of Apocalypse - The Complete Epic (v1 - v4)  (2005 -
description:
X-Men - Age of Apocalypse - The Complete Epic (v1 - v4)  (2005 - 2006)) (digital) (Minutemen-Midas)

A Series of Graphic Novels reprinting the famous Age of Apocalypse storyline.

Volume 1 Reprints: X-Men Chronicles #1 and #2, Tales from the Age of Apocalypse: By the Light, X-Man #-1, X-Man '96 Annual, Tales from the Age of Apocalypse: Sinister Bloodlines, and Blink #1-4

Volume 2 Reprints: X-Men: Alpha, Age of Apocalypse: The Chosen, Generation Next #1, Astonishing X-Men (vol. 1) #1, X-Calibre #1, Gambit and the X-Ternals #1-2, Weapon X (vol. 1) #1-2, Amazing X-Men #1-2, Factor X #1-2, and X-Man #1.

Volume 3 Reprints: Factor X #3, Gambit and the X-Ternals #3, Generation Next #2-3, The Amazing X-Men #2-4, Weapon X #3, X-Calibre #2-3, X-Man (1995) #2-3, and X-Universe (1995) #1.

Volume 4 Reprints: Blink #4, Factor X #4, Gambit and the X-Ternals #4, Generation Next #4, The Amazing X-Men #4, Weapon X #4, X-Calibre #4, X-Man #4, X-Man #53, X-Man #54, X-Men Omega #1, X-Men Prime #1, and X-Universe #2.
